  • java.lang.Object
    • com.querydsl.lucene5.AbstractLuceneQuery<T,Q>

    T - projection type
    Q - concrete subtype of querydsl
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Fetchable<T>, FilteredClause<Q>, SimpleQuery<Q>
    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class AbstractLuceneQuery<T,Q extends AbstractLuceneQuery<T,Q>>
extends Object
implements SimpleQuery<Q>, Fetchable<T>
